title: transfer accounts
body: i transfer my west accoung to eu and i log in and i was lvl 2 and i have nothing in i lost skins worth 500

replies.body:
Are you sure you logged into the correct account? If you had an account on EUW that was level 2, it's possible you logged into that one by accident.

Past that, submit a ticket to player support, we can't really help you here on OCE boards: https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new
